Parameters of fine-mapping analysis

  • Filter out SNPs with MAF <1%
  • Select SNPs within a window of 50kb from the top SNP
  • Estimate LD in EUR sample from 1,000 Genomes
    • filter out SNPs which are not presented in 1,000 Genomes’
  • Run fine-mapping analysis
    • using different tools, PAINTOR or FINEMAP
      • no annotations
    • varying the number of causal variants (1, 3 or 5)
